The budgets are for the Office of Fusion Energy Sciences which is
dominately MFE with about $18 M/year for IFE in the 2000 time frame
and less than $2M/year for IFE in the early 1990s and before.

total MFE dollars through 2000, as-spent:  $8883 M
total spent through 2000 (1992 dollars):  $12856 M


*projected
